flowchart LR
    REQ[API Request]

    REQ --> PAGE{paginated?}
    PAGE -->|yes| CURSOR[cursor-based pagination\nnext_cursor / prev_cursor]
    PAGE -->|no| FULL[full response]

    REQ --> FILTER[filters: field=value\noperators: eq/lt/gt/in/contains]
    REQ --> SORT[sort: field:asc / field:desc]

    CURSOR --> RESP[response: items + cursors]
    FILTER --> RESP
    SORT --> RESP
